nodes.text: Security Hub 1Y-33 was a security station located at the Old World on Zakuul. In 3630 BBY Kaliyo Djannis and the Alliance Commander disabled the Security Hub in preparation for their assault on the Overwatch.
Security Hub 1Y-33 appears on Zakuul during Chapter 10: Anarchy in Paradise of the Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire expansion.
